title: Starting an Online Business For Dummies, 7th edition.pdf
description:
2013 | 456 Pages | ISBN: 1118607783 | PDF | 52 MB

Mind your business with this updated edition of the bestselling online business how-to guide

Have a computer, an Internet connection, and a dream? Then, you're already on your way to starting your very own online business.

This fun and friendly guide can help you turn your big idea into big bucks whether you're expanding your real-world storefront online or creating your own virtual startup.
